---
// About Component - Personal introduction section
---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <span class="section-tag">关于我</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="gradient-text">你好，我是钱磊</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-image fade-up stagger-1">
        <div class="image-wrapper">
          <div class="image-placeholder">
            <span class="avatar-text">L</span>
          </div>
          <div class="image-glow"></div>
          <div class="image-ring"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="floating-icons">
          <div class="icon-bubble icon-1">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
              <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-bubble icon-2">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line>
              <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-bubble icon-3">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-text fade-up stagger-2">
        <p class="about-intro">
          我是钱磊，一名有 <strong>10+ 年研发经验</strong> 的工程师。以前做复杂 Web 和平台工具，现在更认真地做自己的 AI 工具、自动化系统和桌面效率产品。
        </p>

        <p>
          上海大学本科毕业。后来在阿里巴巴、拼多多、美团、字节跳动一路做过大型 Web、前端工程、BFF、研发平台和自动化发布。那段经历给我留下的不是简历标签，而是两件事：把复杂流程拆清楚，把重复工作做成工具。
        </p>

        <p>
          最近我把更多时间放在自己的作品上：<strong>Cairn / DocsGraph</strong> 让文档变成 Agent 可用的上下文，<strong>Lumen Brief</strong> 把 AI 信息源整理进知识库，<strong>MCPort</strong> 把 HTTP API 配成 MCP 工具，<strong>Sotto</strong> 和 <strong>Red Green Light</strong> 则把本地 AI CLI 做进日常桌面。
        </p>

        <div class="evidence-wall" aria-label="过往经历与近期作品">
          <span class="wall-label">Past</span>
          <div class="wall-logos">
            <span class="brand brand-alibaba">Alibaba</span>
            <span class="brand brand-pdd">拼多多</span>
            <span class="brand brand-meituan">美团</span>
            <span class="brand brand-bytedance">ByteDance</span>
          </div>
          <span class="wall-divider"></span>
          <div class="wall-side">
            <span class="side-label">Now</span>
            <span class="brand brand-cairn">Cairn</span>
            <span class="brand brand-mcport">MCPort</span>
            <span class="brand brand-sotto">Sotto</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-highlights">
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>阿里巴巴 / 拼多多 / 美团 / 字节跳动等一线工程经历</span>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>MCP / RAG / Agent 工具调用 / CLI 自动化</span>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>从想法、原型、测试到上线页面</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary about-cta" data-resume-chat aria-label="和我聊聊">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
            <path d="M12 7l1.5 3 3 .4-2.2 2.1.5 3-2.8-1.4-2.8 1.4.5-3L7.5 10.4 10.5 10z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" opacity="0.85"/>
          </svg>
          和我聊聊
          <span class="cta-badge">作品</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-color), transparent);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
  }
  
  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  
  .avatar-text {
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20px;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(40px);
    opacity: 0.4;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: pulse-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .image-ring {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -15px;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: spin-slow 20s linear infinite;
  }
  
  .floating-icons {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -30px;
  }
  
  .icon-bubble {
    position: absolute;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .icon-1 {
    top: 10%;
    right: -10%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }
  
  .icon-2 {
    bottom: 15%;
    left: -15%;
    animation-delay: -2s;
  }
  
  .icon-3 {
    bottom: 5%;
    right: -5%;
    animation-delay: -4s;
  }
  
  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .about-intro {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .about-intro strong {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  
  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  .highlight-item svg {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .about-cta {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .cta-badge {
    margin-left: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25), rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.22));
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* === Company / Logo Wall === */
  .evidence-wall {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .wall-label,
  .internship-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .wall-logos,
  .wall-side {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .wall-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 18px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .brand {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast),
      border-color var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .brand:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .brand-cairn:hover { color: #22d3ee; border-color: #22d3ee; background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08); }
  .brand-lumen:hover { color: #f59e0b; border-color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08); }
  .brand-mcport:hover { color: #8b5cf6; border-color: #8b5cf6; background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08); }
  .brand-sotto:hover { color: #34d399; border-color: #34d399; background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.08); }
  .brand-rgl:hover { color: #ef4444; border-color: #ef4444; background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08); }
  .brand-luma:hover { color: #ec4899; border-color: #ec4899; background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.08); }
  .brand-alibaba:hover { color: #ff6a00; border-color: #ff6a00; background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.08); }
  .brand-pdd:hover { color: #e02e24; border-color: #e02e24; background: rgba(224, 46, 36, 0.08); }
  .brand-meituan:hover { color: #ffd000; border-color: #ffd000; background: rgba(255, 208, 0, 0.08); }
  .brand-bytedance:hover { color: #25f4ee; border-color: #25f4ee; background: rgba(37, 244, 238, 0.08); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .evidence-wall {
      gap: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    }
    .brand {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      padding: 0.15rem 0.45rem;
    }
    .wall-divider {
      display: none;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .about-image {
      order: -1;
    }
    
    .about-highlights {
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .about-cta {
      align-self: center;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .image-wrapper {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
    
    .avatar-text {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
    
    .floating-icons {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
